10-23-'32
5116 Cass SO., 
Omaha Nebraska. 
My sweet girl,
Here I am - all by my lonesome & of course I'm thinking about my dear sweetheart, as usual! You blessed girl, I can't say to the full extenet of my feelings just hwo much I'm missing you! 
Nothing can help me 'til I am once more with you, & satisfied! Dad, Judge Vinsonhaler, & Rev. Plank are all enjoying themselves in a secret manner somewhere in this city! They gave me the Auburn & I've been staying with Mr. Leigh Leslie! Lovely people! They do all they can think of in effort to show me a good time, but Heck! I'm not happy with out the only girl I love! 
Sweetheart, I love you always the same, & I'm so glad 

