that you do realize it! 
Take care of yoruself, be as happy as possible, & always remember the things I've told you about my sincere feelings regarding yourself!
I know you will, & it makes me so happy & grateful! Hope you have received all of my letters, honey! I have never yet missed a day of writing you either a letter or card! 
I have read your sweet letters over & over again, & still am wishing for another one before time is up in Omaha! 
Please, don't think ('cause I haven't answered your letters systematically) that I disregard anything that is in them; be-cause I don't disregard a single word you write! I just haven't answered in detail the things you've written! C? 

139
-3-
I haven't gone to a show here yet & don't suppose I will; be-cause if it's a good show I miss you & wish for you so, that it ruins it for me! You dear girl, I am satisfied with having only you for my happiness!
I feel as happy as any human needs to feel - when I can be with you! Excuse the stationary, dear; but it is all that I could find here at Leslie's home! Please! Remember how i love to hear from you, & that your letters play the im-portant part in keeping me happy! See? Sweetheart!! 
I'm so glad that you enjoyed the trip to <unclear/> with Eny! Did she "kiss" you as much as I always have done?? Ha! Ha! Sweet girl, I'll bet - U - she didn't!! 
I'd give anything to kiss you goodnight each night, but gee 

